{"tid":2442161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2100 眾新聞 中國組 中國石家莊寫字樓大火 外牆疑違規使用易燃物料｜ 中共總書記習近平經濟心腹林毅夫 舉國攻關高科技","createTime":"2021-03-11T07:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T14:22:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df42cdfcf89976b5e424de5221ccc755af75e2d2","tid":2442161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"2100 眾新聞 中國組<br />\n中國石家莊寫字樓大火 外牆疑違規使用易燃物料｜<br />\n中共總書記習近平經濟心腹林毅夫 舉國攻關高科技 成功後低價供應全世界｜<br />\n內地山東拉麵哥爆紅帶動全村賺錢 振興鄉村新出路？<br />\n (眾新聞 中國組) #眾新聞中國組​<br />\n20210310<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OLwBr7weP_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOLwBr7weP_s&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=f13c11b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OLwBr7weP_s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n70.4K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n🔸河北石家莊寫字樓周二發生沖天大火，分析指火勢迅速蔓延，源於外牆保溫層使用易燃物料，存在違規嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n🔸被視為習近平經濟智囊的林毅夫指中國在高科技研發受外界封鎖，會利用舉國體制優勢攻關，一旦衝破瓶頸研發成功，就會低價傾銷反擊。<br />\n<br />\n🔸山東一名「拉麵哥」因為童叟無欺，拉麵多年來只賣3元、不加價而爆紅，更帶動全村發展。"},{"pid":"aba6776c912268e2c0f9213e7e7157db5375d7a2","tid":2442161,"uid":270307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869b1aed28ded3dd0f9a6386f84aacea6f6cd3db","tid":2442161,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8dc590adf012bdd8178c4c8af914804f93b81b0","tid":2442161,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}